Hi Tom,

Get a 51mm hole saw and drill the dash below the radio. The end result 
looks stock!

http://www.pottsfamily.ca/westfakia/VDOgaugeTrio/

It takes some moxy to put a drill to a perfectly good dash, but the end 
results were worth it. Measure several times before you punch the pilot 
holes.

Happy trails,

